      "updated": 1777113282921,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "We need to Ask interviewer thAT IS THE we have limited RAM do we have to save the RAM \nand if we  need to save memory basically RAM we can introduce the fly wight directly  ",
      "fontSize": 20,
