      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1777113338742,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "In RAM We have multiple obejcts created in the RAM \nin millions and RAM is Limited hence to save the RAM \nwe use the fly weight ",
