      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1777114523083,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Any nvlaue like length, width, color etc ki limited possible values honge Means inki \nvalue ek range me hi hogi right, kuch astroid honge je same length, widge and color ke honge right, unka ek object ban sakta\nbut still they can have diffrent positions and speed,\n\nso kuch property ko multiple object me same hongi  - Intrinsix Propert ( Same or reuse )\nkuch property most of the  objects me diffrent unique hi hongi - Extensic Propert ( diffrent or can not reuse )",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Any nvlaue like length, width, color etc ki limited possible values honge Means inki \nvalue ek range me hi hogi right, kuch astroid honge je same length, widge and color ke honge right, unka ek object ban sakta\nbut still they can have diffrent positions and speed,\n\nso kuch property ko multiple object me same hongi  - Intrinsix Propert ( Same or reuse )\nkuch property most of the  objects me diffrent unique hi hongi - Extensic Propert ( diffrent or can not reuse )",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
